Title: As a user I can get all warehouse with a valid path
As a user I can't get all warehouse without path
As a user I can get user profile data with a valid path
As a user I can't get user profile data with an invalid path
As a user I can get warehouse by ID with a valid path
As a user I can't get warehouse by ID without path
As a user I can't get warehouse data with an invalid ID (by entering the ID numbers, letters & symbols at the same time)
As a user I can't get warehouse data with an invalid ID (by entering an ID number that does not yet exist in the database)
